     <target value="No target"></target>
     <actual value="Approximately 29,027,000 people

In 2020, IMS supported a wide range of media content partners to produce reliable public interest content with a key focus on engaging and reaching communities, women, and marginalised groups. The content was made available to the audience at different platforms &#x2013; e.g. radio, TV, print media and online.
The key figures are:
&#x2022; Radio programmes in Somalia reached an estimated audience of up to approximately 6 mio.
&#x2022; Radio programmes in Sahel reached an estimated audience of up to approximately 2 mio.
&#x2022; Start-up media partners on the regional Asia programme collectively reached an estimated audience of approximately 12,742,000 million people
&#x2022; On the country programmes in Pakistan and Myanmar an estimated audience of approximately 7,800,000 were reached
&#x2022; Online, approximately 485,000 people were reached across the Sahel and Somalia programmes"></actual>
    </period>
   </indicator>
  </result>
